 2HELP GROUP0

 2--- General ---0

 Groups are sets of users.  Messages, Rooms, and Hallways can be limited
to a selected group, and users may belong to more than one group.
 Group only rooms have a ":" after the room name instead of the normal ">"
charachter.

 2--- Using groups ---0
 
 .ELM  -- Enter Limited-access Message
 .EG   -- Enter Group only message
 .ELR  -- Enter Limited-access room

 After these, you will be prompted for a group name.  You can limit
a message or room to any group which you are a member of.  To find
out which groups you belong to, use the Read Configuration command
noted elsewhere.

